Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
all_hold_analysis_views(25.10)                  all_hold_analysis_views(25.10)

Name
       all_hold_analysis_views  - Returns a Tcl list of all active hold analy-
       sis views in the design

Syntax
       all_hold_analysis_views

       Returns a Tcl list of all active hold analysis views in the design.

       Use this command after setting active hold analysis views for  the  de-
       sign (set_analysis_view).

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

Example
              * The following command defines the active setup and hold analy-
                sis views for the design:

                set_analysis_view  -setup  {missionWCCOM  mission2WCCOM} -hold
                {missionBCCOM testBCCOM}

              * The following command returns a list of the active hold analy-
                sis views in the design:

                all_hold_analysis_views

                The software returns the following results:

                {missionBCCOM testBCCOM}

Related Information
              * set_analysis_view

              * create_analysis_view

              * all_analysis_views

